  "title": "Business News Journalist/Correspondent (Zaobao)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Job</strong></p>\n<p>As a business news journalist/correspondent, you are expected to gather facts and information through research and interviews and report the information in a clear, concise and exciting way in the print article and digital format.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree holder, preferably in business, finance, economics, and accountancy</li>\n  <li>Effectively bilingual in Chinese and English, with excellent writing, translation, and conversational skills</li>\n  <li>Possess a curious mind with a nose for news and scoops</li>\n  <li>Has a strong interest in business news and current affairs</li>\n  <li>Must be driven, independent, reliable, and highly adaptable to changes</li>\n  <li>Possess the ability to excel with autonomy and ambiguity</li>\n  <li>Meticulous, accurate, and result-oriented, and demonstrates the ability to work under pressure and meet tight deadlines</li>\n  <li>Sensitive to numbers and data</li>\n  <li>Possess the ability to break down complex ideas and make them easy to understand for different target audiences/stakeholders</li>\n</ul>",
